title: OIP-18: Reward rate framework and reduction
body:
### Summary
 - introduce a new reward rate framework to guide Policy decisions and align community expectations
 - as part of the framework, the Policy team proposes a reward rate reduction to 0.2975%, from a current 0.35% of total supply, which is an approximate APY of 8,000% (changes with % of OHM staked, is not static)

### Framework
![](https://i.imgur.com/RwZzYFt.png)

Additional context, explanation and discussion of this proposal can be found on the forum:

https://forum.olympusdao.finance/d/77-oip-18-reward-rate-framework-and-reduction

### Vote
**Option (1)**: Adopt framework and reduce reward rate to 0.2975%
**Option (2)**: Don’t adopt framework, but reduce reward rate to 0.2975%
**Option (3)**: Don’t adopt framework and don’t reduce reward rate to 0.2975%

If the proposal passes the changes would come into effect immediately.
